# Unit Overview

#### In the Creating Apps with Devices unit, students explore the role of physical devices in computing. Using **App Lab** and the **BBC micro:bit**, students develop programs that utilize the same hardware inputs and outputs that you see in the smart devices, looking at how a simple rough prototype can lead to a finished product. Then, students explore how physical devices can be used to react to the world around them using a ‚Äúmaker‚Äù mindset to create prototypes with everyday materials.
</p></div>

